[ Help - developer in trouble ]

- ecasound compiles on FreeBSD (4.7), Solaris (2.6-2.8) and Cygwin;
  how about other UNIX platforms (other BSDs, OS X, IRIX, AIX)?
- ecasound compiles out-of-the-box on Redhat (6-8) and PLD Linux
  systems, what about other Linux distros?
